<HEADLINE> First International Hardware Show Opens in HK </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 28 (Xinhua) -- The first international
hardware show opened today at the Convention and Exhibition Center
of Hong Kong.
</P>
<P>
