<HEADLINE> French Stock Tumbles by 9 Percent in Opening </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, October 28 (Xinhua) -- The Paris stock exchange opened
today with a 9.09 percent tumble of its CAC 40 index, amid a
worldwide near crash of stock markets.
</P>
