</P>
<P>
-- Gordon Brown set Britain on course for membership of the
European single currency yesterday - but he ruled out any
likelihood of it happening within five years.
</P>
<P>
The Financial Times:
</P>
<P>
-- The extent of Wall Street's slide came as a shock to dealers
