<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, October 27 (Xinhua) -- Ukrainian President Leonid
Danilovich Kuchma announced Sunday night that he would enter the
next presidential election set for October, 1999.
</P>
<P>
He expressed confidence in a television speech that Ukraine's
economy would change for the better by the next election.
</P>
<P>
Earlier, he said he would participate in the election provided
the national economy would be improved.
</P>
<P>
