<HEADLINE> Ukraine, NATO to Discuss Cooperation </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KIEV, October 27 (Xinhua) -- Delegates of the North Atlantic
Treaty Organization (NATO)' political committee arrived here today
for a two-day visit to discuss Ukrainian-NATO cooperation.
</P>
<P>
