commissioner for political affairs and director of the alliance's
political directorate, and the Ukrainian inter-departmental
commission for cooperation with NATO will hold talks and are
expected to develop a new European security architecture.
</P>
<P>
The delegation will also meet officials of the Ukrainian
Foreign Ministry to discuss the development of Ukrainian-NATO
cooperation and the implementation of the Special Partnership
Charter. 
