<HEADLINE> Gap at Yellow River Dam Site Near Join-up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XIAOLANGDI (Yellow River), October 28 (Xinhua) -- By 8:30
a.m. today, the gap of the Yellow River at the Xiaolangdi Dam
constuction site has been narrowed to 10.59 meters, according to
an official at the project headquarters.
</P>
<P>
The rate of flow today was 58 cu.m. per second moving at a
speed of 4.7 meters per second, faster than yesterday's flow, but
officials say this presents no problem.
</P>
