<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, October 28 (Xinhua) -- The People's Bank of China
today issued the market exchange rates in RMB yuan against three
major currencies. The middle price of the RMB against convertible
currencies is mainly based on the closing price of the preceding
interbank trading.
</P>
<P>
